{"results":[{"aya":"085","id":5064,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"我比你们更临近他，但你们不晓得，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"086","id":5065,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"如果你们不是受报应的，--","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"087","id":5066,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"你们怎不使灵魂复返于本位呢？如果你们是说实话的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"088","id":5067,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"如果他是被眷顾的，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"089","id":5068,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"那末，他将享受舒适、给养与恩泽的乐园；","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"090","id":5069,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"如果他是幸福者，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"091","id":5070,"locale":"zh","sura":"056","text":"那末，一般幸福的人将对他说：祝你平安！","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":14,"previousPage":"/zh/s056-12.json","nextPage":"/zh/s056-14.json"}}